text: Novotaishevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Imendyashevsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 25 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 48 km from Krasnousolsky, 4 km from Karagayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Novotaishevo
